<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>lsh bạgẖfr</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- knt sẖạrd knt wḥdy rwḥy ḍlt rjly zlt
 md ạ̹ydh wḍm ydy qạlly ʿdy lw btkẖṭy qwm wkẖṭy
 qwm nạdyny bṣ jnbk sẖwf bqlbk hạtlạqyny lsh bạgẖfr
 ạlqrạr- lsh ʿndy bywt ktyrẗ lsh mftwḥẗ ạlḥẓyrẗ ạdkẖl ạskn
 lw tjyny hạtlạqyny lsh bạgẖfr
 2- knt brdạn knt mḥny knt msẖ sẖạyf wkẖạyf
 kẖd ḥmwly ạlqạsyẗ mny sẖạlhạ ʿny qạlly sẖạyf
 qlby ʿạrf fyn bnyny bṣ jnbk sẖwf bqlbk hạtlạqyny lsh bạgẖfr</lyrics>
